her hair will return to its original
color and her evil ways will cease.

8
00:00:52,509 --> 00:00:53,762
Cho Yi Hang guarded the flower
on Mount Shin Fung

9
00:00:53,887 --> 00:00:57,890
and vowed to remain until it blossomed,
in hopes of reuniting with his beloved.

10
00:01:55,156 --> 00:01:58,367
Ni Chang, as soon as
