571
01:07:30,887 --> 01:07:31,514
This is from me!

572
01:07:37,643 --> 01:07:39,853
Now you know what a real man is!

573
01:07:45,235 --> 01:07:46,527
This is from Yee!

574
01:07:51,448 --> 01:07:53,118
Forget about me.
Just go!

575
01:07:53,201 --> 01:07:54,034
Don't!

576
01:08:01,918 --> 01:08:03,837
Liu.

577
01:08:09,300 --> 01:08:11,761
Kit..
l've done my best...

578
01:08:12,929 --> 01:08:14,514
Liu!

579
01:08:31,613 --> 01:08:35,076
l just have to see
how strong true love really is!

580
01:08:52,427 --> 01:08:53,511
Kit.

581
01:08:57,806 --> 01:08:58,557
Kit.


582
01:09:01,644 --> 01:09:04,605
Lyre.
You woke up from the spell?

583
01:09:13,407 --> 01:09:14,867
l want you to kill him
with your own hands!

584
01:09:16,659 --> 01:09:18,662
No.
l won't do it!

585
01:09:28,130 --> 01:09:29,380
No!

586
01:09:59,076 --> 01:10:05,582
Lyre!

587
01:10:12,506 --> 01:10:13,757
Kit!

588
01:10:22,891 --> 01:10:26,646
So you can't part from each other?
l will let you two die together!

589
01:10:27,398 --> 01:10:28,148
Run!

590
01:10:35,197 --> 01:10:36,864
Lyre, run!

591
01:11:18,238 --> 01:11:19,157
Uncle Cho!

592
01:12:00,864 --> 01:12:01,617
Ni Chang.

593
01:12:08,747 --> 01:12:09,832
lt's all my fault.

594
01:12:15,755 --> 01:12:16,672
Let them go.

595
01:12:18,966 --> 01:12:21,429
Why didn't you say these words
ten years ago?

596
01:12:21,761 --> 01:12:23,014
lt's too late now!

597
01:12:27,350 --> 01:12:28,726
Go to hell,
you witch!

598
01:13:04,720 --> 01:13:05,805
Uncle Cho!

599
01:13:08,057 --> 01:13:08,850
Uncle Cho!

600
01:13:11,186 --> 01:13:11,978
Kit!

601
01:13:15,899 --> 01:13:17,192
Why don't you fight back?

602
01:13:22,698 --> 01:13:23,323
Ni Chang.

603
01:13:25,909 --> 01:13:27,201
No matter what wrong l've done,

604
01:13:29,579 --> 01:13:34,167
l just want you to know
that l didn't mean to betray you.

605
01:13:44,344 --> 01:13:45,011
Don't move!

606
01:13:45,387 --> 01:13:47,972
Once the hair leaves you,
you'll die!

607
01:14:11,037 --> 01:14:16,418
Witch, to get you this flower, Uncle Cho
waited on Mount Shin Fung for ten years!

608
01:14:16,960 --> 01:14:18,378
And you still want to kill him?

609
01:14:30,764 --> 01:14:32,684
Yi Hang!
Don't move!

610
01:15:11,639 --> 01:15:14,851
Ni Chang!
You paved your own road of destruction.

611
01:15:15,351 --> 01:15:19,648
Do you remember what l said? No one
will have a happy ending with you.

612
01:15:52,014 --> 01:15:55,265
l thought l'd never see you again
in this lifetime.

613
01:16:09,113 --> 01:16:11,117
Have l aged much?

614
01:16:15,412 --> 01:16:20,166
No matter how you've changed,
lt's not important to me.

615
01:16:23,211 --> 01:16:26,966
l've become this way,
all because you did not trust me.

616
01:16:31,720 --> 01:16:32,470
Forgive me!

617
01:16:36,807 --> 01:16:42,815
Hate and despair

618
01:16:44,398 --> 01:16:50,195
Who knew love could be so hard

619
01:16:51,613 --> 01:16:57,369
Love and hate l cannot resolve

620
01:16:58,620 --> 01:17:05,295
Passion faded and youth consumed

621
01:17:06,297 --> 01:17:13,219
All at once l held in my hand
The past and the future

622
01:17:13,552 --> 01:17:20,603
Can we call this
love everlasting?

623
01:17:21,145 --> 01:17:37,827
l do believe when parting
your embrace will sooth my sorrow

624
01:17:54,094 --> 01:17:58,472
Liu, that day at Mount Shin Fung,
we actually found Uncle Cho.

625
01:18:05,063 --> 01:18:05,815
