626
01:18:07,648 --> 01:18:09,567
Kit, the other day
at the evil palace,

627
01:18:09,652 --> 01:18:12,404
l thought l saw
the white hair witch's hair turn black!

628
01:18:12,779 --> 01:18:13,363
